Meet Our Contributors - Ask Us Anything! When Slack seems like it’s going too fast, and you just need a quick answer from a human&hellip;
Meet Our Contributors gives you a monthly one-hour opportunity to ask questions about our upstream community, watch interviews with our contributors, and participate in peer code reviews.
When: Every first Wednesday of the month at the following times. Grab a copy of the calendar to yours from kubernetes.
